description: This waterfront penthouse unit located directly across from the beach offers all the views and ocean breeze. Large front and back exclusive decks in this rarely available location with 3 bedrooms and 1300 sq feet of living space and nice original touches of period detail throughout. Walk to Castle Island, Farragut Park and Broadway. 1st showings at Sunday Open House.
